多次成功抵禦諸葛亮北伐 <br />\n猜中諸葛亮政事繁忙 扙責20以上咸決於亮 所啖食不至三升 一定好快死<br />\n結果不久病逝五丈原<br />\n<br />\n世人皆以為死諸葛驚走活仲達 如果繼續南下滅蜀 死的將會係整個司馬家<br />\n因為狡兔死走狗烹 睇到的並非一時之利 而係諗埋如何應付朝廷的政治鬥爭<br />\n<br />\n遼東燕國叛亂 迅速剿滅<br />\n<br />\n朝廷被曹爽批鬥排斥 72歲之高齡扮病重暗中發動高平陵事變 夷滅曹爽三族<br />\n掌管整個魏室 壽春第一叛殺王凌 為晉朝鋪路<br />\n<br />\n司馬懿計算好深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wKTSAbX1AWY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwKTSAbX1AWY&d=xTomnt8%2Fnx7TIgb7e0FxbE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=c3e645f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wKTSAbX1AWY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vzf_fDX0M58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVzf_fDX0M58&d=xTomnt8%2Fnx7TIgb7e0FxbE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=6dd68da5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vzf_fDX0M58</a><br />\n扮老弱隱藏又得<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vdENw4Yv2yk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvdENw4Yv2yk&d=xTomnt8%2Fnx7TIgb7e0FxbE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=b2b2de4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vdENw4Yv2yk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EQj9j1yoFrc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEQj9j1yoFrc&d=xTomnt8%2Fnx7TIgb7e0FxbE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=8f815e03\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EQj9j1yoFrc</a><br />\n扮到成個日本武士又得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T06:10:30.000Z",